      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row letter-paragraph">
      <div class="col-12">
        <p>Even while being thousands of miles away in Panama, our partners held regular video conferences to make sure that input from all three of our family members was heard throughout the design and building process. We couldn’t be more proud of our fresh, contemporary and cozy place.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row letter-paragraph">
